WEBVTT

1
00:00:15.950 --> 00:00:17.890
(Lee Jun Young)

2
00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:25.660
(Lee Ju Myoung)

3
00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:34.340
(Jeon Hye Jin. Jin Goo)

4
00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:51.920
(Reborn Rookie)

5
00:00:55.250 --> 00:00:56.520
- Charge to 200.
- Clear.

6
00:00:56.790 --> 00:00:57.790
- Clear.
- Clear.

7
00:01:16.510 --> 00:01:17.640
Don't you dare die.

8
00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.950
If you die. I'll never forgive you.

9
00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:32.190
Jun Hyeon.

10
00:01:32.930 --> 00:01:33.930
Jun Hyeon. are you okay?

11
00:01:39.670 --> 00:01:42.230
How is Chairman Kang?

12
00:01:42.730 --> 00:01:43.740
Oh. gosh.

13
00:01:47.910 --> 00:01:48.910
Honey!

14
00:01:56.650 --> 00:01:57.850
Honey.

15
00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:01.120
March 6. 2026.

16
00:02:02.090 --> 00:02:03.260
Time. 8:42pm.

17
00:02:04.060 --> 00:02:05.090
Patient Kang Yong Ho...

18
00:02:06.890 --> 00:02:08.160
has been pronounced dead.

19
00:02:15.530 --> 00:02:16.540
Mom.

20
00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:20.710
Bang Geul...

21
00:02:21.410 --> 00:02:24.010
Bang Geul. your poor father...

22
00:02:26.010 --> 00:02:28.410
Your poor father. What are we going to do?

23
00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:39.660
Don't!

24
00:02:40.330 --> 00:02:41.590
My dad isn't dead.

25
00:02:42.130 --> 00:02:44.430
Dad. I'm here.

26
00:02:45.160 --> 00:02:47.930
Open your eyes. Your
youngest daughter is here.

27
00:02:50.570 --> 00:02:52.670
Open your eyes. please!

28
00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:08.749
Why are you giving up already? Do more!

29
00:03:08.750 --> 00:03:10.390
You have to do everything you can.

30
00:03:10.690 --> 00:03:14.230
Put him on life support. Do
whatever it takes to save him!

31
00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:19.830
Do not disrespect the deceased.
You are not a family member.

32
00:03:25.100 --> 00:03:27.470
Mom!

33
00:03:28.540 --> 00:03:29.570
Help!

34
00:03:30.110 --> 00:03:32.580
Somebody. help! Mom.

35
00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:39.080
(VIP Ward)

36
00:03:41.350 --> 00:03:43.190
We begin with breaking news.

37
00:03:43.260 --> 00:03:45.220
We're reporting the death of Kang Yong Ho.

38
00:03:45.290 --> 00:03:46.790
the Chairman of the Choiseong Group.

39
00:03:47.130 --> 00:03:50.600
Chairman Kang Yong Ho. a
legend of the Korean economy...

40
00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.800
passed away today.

41
00:03:53.130 --> 00:03:55.500
The Chairman had been
receiving treatment...

42
00:03:55.570 --> 00:03:58.970
- while in a coma for a long time...
- Get out of my way. you jerk!

43
00:04:03.510 --> 00:04:04.540
How could you...

44
00:04:05.340 --> 00:04:07.080
How could you do this. Kang Jae Gyeong?

45
00:04:07.910 --> 00:04:09.210
How could you...

46
00:04:10.820 --> 00:04:12.650
kill Father with your own hands?

47
00:04:16.290 --> 00:04:18.090
You just had to see it through. didn't you?

48
00:04:20.690 --> 00:04:24.100
Even if it's a position you
got with blood on your hands.

49
00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.530
you don't care as long as you get it?

50
00:04:27.700 --> 00:04:31.400
Do you feel no remorse
for what you did to Father?

51
00:04:39.710 --> 00:04:43.320
Stop blaming me and
get a grip on the situation.

52
00:04:43.880 --> 00:04:45.950
Because you were foolish
enough to join Kang Bang Geul...

53
00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:48.750
and frame Father for the slush fund.

54
00:04:49.420 --> 00:04:51.520
all of Choiseong is about
to come under attack.

55
00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:53.829
- What?
- Didn't you expect this much...

56
00:04:53.830 --> 00:04:55.090
when you sold Father out?

57
00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:57.660
Instead of our late father.
you and I are the ones...

58
00:04:57.730 --> 00:04:58.730
who'll be torn to shreds.

59
00:04:59.330 --> 00:05:01.000
If you want to pull yourself
together and survive.

60
00:05:01.470 --> 00:05:02.900
cut your ties now.

61
00:05:03.740 --> 00:05:07.310
The people our dead father
will drag down with him aren't us.

62
00:05:07.670 --> 00:05:09.410
It's Butler Jo and Kang Bang Geul.

63
00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:13.950
- You're unbelievable.
- Are you going to let everything...

64
00:05:14.010 --> 00:05:15.550
with the Choiseong name on it collapse?

65
00:05:15.610 --> 00:05:19.220
Is that why you killed Father?
Just to save your own skin?

66
00:05:21.620 --> 00:05:22.620
You know it.

67
00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:26.120
"Protect Choiseong
no matter what it takes."

68
00:05:30.060 --> 00:05:32.930
I'm just carrying out Father's
will as if it were divine order.

69
00:05:34.230 --> 00:05:35.500
The way we turned out...

70
00:05:36.500 --> 00:05:37.700
It's all Father's fault.

71
00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:46.980
Do what you do best. Use Bang Geul.

72
00:05:48.850 --> 00:05:51.820
We'll go down as the poor
children of the first wife...

73
00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:55.720
who almost lost their inheritance
to the second wife's schemes.

74
00:05:57.720 --> 00:06:01.790
Otherwise. our entire lives...

75
00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:06.000
spent fighting for Choiseong
will seem so pathetic.

76
00:06:14.340 --> 00:06:15.940
We have to protect what's ours.

77
00:06:17.810 --> 00:06:18.840
Jae Seong.

78
00:06:25.020 --> 00:06:27.290
Stop tormenting me. Father.

79
00:06:29.020 --> 00:06:31.720
You had your lifetime to order
everyone around. Isn't that enough?

80
00:06:32.190 --> 00:06:34.330
How long are you going to stand in my way?

81
00:06:34.590 --> 00:06:35.930
What is there left to hold on to?

82
00:06:38.760 --> 00:06:39.760
Let me...

83
00:06:40.630 --> 00:06:41.770
put an end to it for you.

84
00:07:13.270 --> 00:07:14.270
Who are you?

85
00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:32.320
Is it true he died of cardiac arrest?

86
00:07:32.380 --> 00:07:33.590
Has he been medically declared dead?

87
00:07:33.650 --> 00:07:35.350
Is the cause of death
confirmed to be natural?

88
00:07:35.420 --> 00:07:37.860
- Are there plans for an autopsy?
- Did his condition suddenly worsen?

89
00:07:37.990 --> 00:07:40.660
There were reports his condition
had recently improved. Is that true?

90
00:07:41.690 --> 00:07:44.430
The patient had been in a
coma for over two months.

91
00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:47.670
We administered various
subsequent treatments.

92
00:07:48.870 --> 00:07:51.140
but he passed away a short while ago.

93
00:07:51.200 --> 00:07:53.170
We heard he briefly regained consciousness.

94
00:07:53.470 --> 00:07:55.870
Is there any reason why his
condition suddenly worsened?

95
00:07:56.110 --> 00:07:57.440
Was there really no chance of recovery?

96
00:07:57.510 --> 00:07:58.640
What was the exact cause of death?

97
00:07:58.710 --> 00:07:59.840
Were there complications during treatment?

98
00:07:59.910 --> 00:08:00.910
That's President Kang Jae Gyeong.

99
00:08:08.690 --> 00:08:10.060
{\an8}Could you give us a comment?

100
00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:11.390
{\an8}Where is President Kang Jae Seong?

101
00:08:12.060 --> 00:08:15.130
{\an8}- Where is President Kang Jae Seong?
- How are you feeling right now?

102
00:08:15.190 --> 00:08:16.590
{\an8}How are you holding up?

103
00:08:17.230 --> 00:08:18.300
{\an8}Excuse me. please let us through.

104
00:08:25.840 --> 00:08:26.840
This man...

105
00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:30.810
As his physician. he did his best.

106
00:08:31.580 --> 00:08:33.410
Instead of pointless speculation.

107
00:08:34.110 --> 00:08:35.110
please allow...

108
00:08:36.050 --> 00:08:37.820
the deceased to depart in peace.

109
00:08:42.350 --> 00:08:43.690
I ask this of you.

110
00:08:48.790 --> 00:08:50.500
Will the company switch to an
emergency management system?

111
00:08:50.530 --> 00:08:52.630
- Please give us a comment.
- Will you make a statement today?

112
00:08:54.970 --> 00:08:57.300
Was every single tear calculated?

113
00:09:00.970 --> 00:09:03.270
Did you hate me so much...

114
00:09:06.910 --> 00:09:08.280
to go so far as to use my death?

115
00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:11.620
What on earth...

116
00:09:14.650 --> 00:09:16.890
was I to you. Jae Gyeong?

117
00:09:22.260 --> 00:09:24.100
(Heo Ok Sun)

118
00:09:24.260 --> 00:09:27.330
(SOS Request. Emergency Rescue Required)

119
00:09:45.550 --> 00:09:46.890
(260 Hwayeon-ro. Deokwon-gu)

120
00:09:48.020 --> 00:09:49.190
(Heo Ok Sun)

121
00:09:53.530 --> 00:09:54.530
Darn it.

122
00:09:55.390 --> 00:09:56.630
Where is she?

123
00:09:58.500 --> 00:09:59.830
Heo Ok Sun!

124
00:10:01.700 --> 00:10:03.230
Answer me!

125
00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:10.440
No!

126
00:10:13.510 --> 00:10:17.150
No!

127
00:10:25.420 --> 00:10:26.420
Are you okay?

128
00:10:27.890 --> 00:10:29.390
Come on. wake up.

129
00:10:30.460 --> 00:10:31.700
Open your eyes!

130
00:10:34.200 --> 00:10:35.730
Grandma. your grandson is here.

131
00:10:36.530 --> 00:10:38.200
Hwang Jun Hyeon is here!

132
00:10:38.800 --> 00:10:39.800
Please...

133
00:10:42.140 --> 00:10:44.180
Please. open your eyes.

134
00:10:45.940 --> 00:10:47.750
Oh. my dear child...

135
00:10:50.820 --> 00:10:52.650
My dear boy...

136
00:10:53.450 --> 00:10:54.550
You're here?

137
00:10:58.820 --> 00:11:00.630
What are you doing here?

138
00:11:01.430 --> 00:11:02.790
You almost got hurt.

139
00:11:09.970 --> 00:11:13.070
Have you eaten?

140
00:11:16.070 --> 00:11:17.910
Did my boy have something to eat?

141
00:11:29.890 --> 00:11:30.990
I'm sorry.

142
00:11:33.530 --> 00:11:35.460
This is all my fault.

143
00:11:38.330 --> 00:11:40.030
I was wrong.

144
00:11:41.100 --> 00:11:42.900
No.

145
00:11:44.270 --> 00:11:45.370
My child.

146
00:11:46.140 --> 00:11:47.270
My child.

147
00:11:50.280 --> 00:11:51.410
You did well.

148
00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:55.110
I'm sorry.

149
00:11:59.480 --> 00:12:00.550
I'm sorry.

150
00:12:29.750 --> 00:12:31.250
(Bongdo Elementary School)

151
00:12:53.500 --> 00:12:55.710
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

152
00:13:07.290 --> 00:13:10.260
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

153
00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:29.710
Ok Sun! I'm late. I'm skipping breakfast!

154
00:13:34.410 --> 00:13:37.480
No. Hey. Just have one bite.

155
00:13:37.550 --> 00:13:41.050
- It's your favourite. galbitang.
- But I'm really late.

156
00:13:44.890 --> 00:13:47.490
- Good boy.
- I'm really off now.

157
00:13:47.590 --> 00:13:49.590
Go to bed without me tonight.
Grandma. I have night practice.

158
00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:51.960
Okay. Be careful and don't get hurt.

159
00:13:52.260 --> 00:13:55.830
Hey. kick the ball hard
and score a lot of goals!

160
00:13:56.200 --> 00:13:58.200
- You got this! Okay.
- I got this!

161
00:14:00.510 --> 00:14:01.840
Turn! That's it.

162
00:14:10.820 --> 00:14:12.020
Jun Hyeon.

163
00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:15.219
Jun Hyeon. come on. Hurry and eat.

164
00:14:15.220 --> 00:14:16.850
Come on and eat.

165
00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:19.490
- Ta-da.
- Gosh. look at these side dishes.

166
00:14:19.890 --> 00:14:21.730
- Looks delicious.
- It's fried tofu rice ball.

167
00:14:21.860 --> 00:14:23.160
- It looks so good.
- Here.

168
00:14:23.230 --> 00:14:25.130
- It looks delicious.
- Take this.

169
00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:26.830
- Pass them around.
- There's fried shrimp too.

170
00:14:26.900 --> 00:14:27.900
Give one to this guy.

171
00:14:37.880 --> 00:14:39.880
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

172
00:15:04.470 --> 00:15:07.610
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

173
00:15:17.180 --> 00:15:21.620
I finally understand why you
wrote that you wanted Choiseong...

174
00:15:24.620 --> 00:15:26.060
on the corporate check.

175
00:15:27.590 --> 00:15:28.630
I finally do.

176
00:15:55.390 --> 00:15:58.860
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

177
00:16:17.310 --> 00:16:20.280
Jae Gyeong. you did this. didn't
you? How could you be so cruel?

178
00:16:20.710 --> 00:16:23.780
He's your father. The
very man who gave you life.

179
00:16:25.750 --> 00:16:28.020
And you dared to act like a
mother with all this hypocrisy?

180
00:16:28.950 --> 00:16:32.020
You know. if you had just
made me chairman back then.

181
00:16:32.460 --> 00:16:34.760
he wouldn't have gone
in such a pathetic way.

182
00:16:35.160 --> 00:16:37.460
Dad wasn't someone
who would just die like that.

183
00:16:37.530 --> 00:16:38.700
It's too strange that
the hospital's CCTV...

184
00:16:38.760 --> 00:16:40.400
was down right at that moment.

185
00:16:40.830 --> 00:16:44.240
Someone even saw you
leaving Dad's hospital room last.

186
00:16:45.700 --> 00:16:48.110
Jae Gyeong. did you really...

187
00:16:49.040 --> 00:16:51.410
do this to your own father?

188
00:16:54.510 --> 00:16:55.510
Did you?

189
00:16:57.980 --> 00:16:59.150
If I said no.

190
00:17:00.450 --> 00:17:01.620
would you even believe me?

191
00:17:06.760 --> 00:17:07.960
I'm ordering an autopsy.

192
00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:12.160
I'm going to find out
the exact cause of death!

193
00:17:12.500 --> 00:17:13.600
Suit yourself.

194
00:17:14.130 --> 00:17:15.130
But...

195
00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:19.740
consider your last debt paid with this.

196
00:17:20.140 --> 00:17:23.510
But you'll be paying back
today's debt several times over.

197
00:17:29.650 --> 00:17:32.280
Where are you going? Stop right there!

198
00:17:32.850 --> 00:17:34.090
Stop right there!

199
00:17:47.530 --> 00:17:48.600
Kang Jae Gyeong!

200
00:17:50.500 --> 00:17:51.540
Get out of my way.

201
00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:53.570
- I said. get out of my way!
- Just you wait.

202
00:17:53.700 --> 00:17:55.470
I won't let Dad go like this.

203
00:17:56.840 --> 00:17:58.280
(Jo Haeng Mun. Audit Team Team Leader)

204
00:18:00.210 --> 00:18:01.250
Did you find it?

205
00:18:03.810 --> 00:18:05.720
There's no camera footage.

206
00:18:06.050 --> 00:18:07.250
Nothing?

207
00:18:07.590 --> 00:18:09.390
It's too strange that
the hospital's CCTV...

208
00:18:09.450 --> 00:18:10.450
was down right at that moment.

209
00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:14.030
Someone even saw you
leaving Dad's hospital room last.

210
00:18:14.290 --> 00:18:15.590
If it wasn't them...

211
00:18:16.130 --> 00:18:17.329
What about the personal
seal and the bankbook?

212
00:18:17.330 --> 00:18:19.700
I got them. I also have...

213
00:18:20.460 --> 00:18:22.900
the real estate documents in their names.

214
00:18:22.970 --> 00:18:24.540
so we have more than
enough to build our case.

215
00:18:24.640 --> 00:18:25.769
We don't have much time.

216
00:18:25.770 --> 00:18:27.870
- Do it as fast as possible.
- Understood.

217
00:18:31.280 --> 00:18:32.810
The board of directors and
the company presidents...

218
00:18:32.880 --> 00:18:33.880
are all standing by.

219
00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:35.710
Tell the legal team to join too.

220
00:18:36.080 --> 00:18:38.050
We need to coordinate the
timing for opening the will.

221
00:18:38.550 --> 00:18:39.580
Yes. ma'am.

222
00:18:47.060 --> 00:18:49.130
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

223
00:18:50.830 --> 00:18:52.160
Dad. aren't you sad?

224
00:18:53.260 --> 00:18:55.230
Grandpa passed away.

225
00:18:55.970 --> 00:18:59.700
My mom and dad don't seem very sad either.

226
00:19:00.170 --> 00:19:01.510
It's all so strange.

227
00:19:02.770 --> 00:19:05.040
I guess they all have something to hide.

228
00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:09.750
Take the kids and wait in the car.

229
00:19:20.220 --> 00:19:22.360
Why would you say something
like that in front of the kids?

230
00:19:22.490 --> 00:19:25.060
You sided with Kang Bang
Geul and sold out your own father.

231
00:19:25.260 --> 00:19:27.330
And who was it that never
once came to visit me?

232
00:19:27.970 --> 00:19:29.170
Is that what your father told you to do?

233
00:19:29.230 --> 00:19:32.070
Don't tell me you still suspect my father.

234
00:19:32.470 --> 00:19:34.910
You were even tailing my father the
day you kidnapped Kang Jae Gyeong.

235
00:19:35.040 --> 00:19:36.510
And you know that's why this
whole mess happened. right?

236
00:19:36.540 --> 00:19:41.050
That's because I was worried Kang
Jae Gyeong would side with Taeha.

237
00:19:41.810 --> 00:19:43.609
Don't you think your father
acquired the hydrogen business...

238
00:19:43.610 --> 00:19:45.020
just because Kang Jae
Gyeong talked him into it?

239
00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:48.350
I doubt she sold it to him cheap.

240
00:19:49.590 --> 00:19:52.420
I wouldn't know. That's all business.

241
00:19:52.820 --> 00:19:54.629
I even thought you got
released from the prosecution...

242
00:19:54.630 --> 00:19:56.430
because Kang Jae
Gyeong pulled some strings.

243
00:19:56.630 --> 00:20:01.400
I worried your father had teamed up
with Kang Jae Gyeong to abandon me.

244
00:20:02.900 --> 00:20:04.300
You have no idea how hurt I was.

245
00:20:05.500 --> 00:20:07.370
I was released because I'm innocent.

246
00:20:08.210 --> 00:20:09.370
Don't worry!

247
00:20:09.870 --> 00:20:11.980
I can't stand Kang Jae Gyeong either.

248
00:20:14.580 --> 00:20:15.750
Did you two come here to fight?

249
00:20:21.020 --> 00:20:24.190
If you're not here to mourn.
then be quiet and leave.

250
00:20:25.220 --> 00:20:27.690
I know you didn't get
to live with him for long.

251
00:20:28.230 --> 00:20:31.360
but aren't you sad? You
haven't shed a single tear.

252
00:20:31.530 --> 00:20:34.370
Will crying bring my
dead father back to life?

253
00:20:36.670 --> 00:20:37.970
Now I know for sure.

254
00:20:38.270 --> 00:20:40.440
You really are just like Kang Jae Gyeong.

255
00:20:40.500 --> 00:20:42.269
I'm done treating you like a person.

256
00:20:42.270 --> 00:20:44.440
What? Why you little...

257
00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:48.010
Get lost. Dad wouldn't want
to see you either. so get lost.

258
00:20:50.580 --> 00:20:52.380
She's completely out of line now.

259
00:20:53.750 --> 00:20:54.890
Let's just go.

260
00:20:55.590 --> 00:20:58.460
Don't waste your breath on her. Move.

261
00:21:06.730 --> 00:21:08.100
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

262
00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:15.440
I'm still not sure if it's okay
for us not to go to the memorial.

263
00:21:15.740 --> 00:21:17.610
Do you think I feel good about it?

264
00:21:18.140 --> 00:21:20.540
But regardless. we have to
get this situation under control.

265
00:21:20.780 --> 00:21:24.550
You all know he never had a
single financial scandal his entire life.

266
00:21:24.780 --> 00:21:27.650
It seems pretty obvious
who the real culprit is.

267
00:21:27.750 --> 00:21:29.450
Whether it's Kang Jae
Seong or Kang Jae Gyeong.

268
00:21:29.520 --> 00:21:31.360
we need to find the source
of the slush fund and...

269
00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:36.630
We must.

270
00:21:37.290 --> 00:21:38.360
And they must be punished.

271
00:21:41.700 --> 00:21:44.700
I'm curious as well. I want
to know who orchestrated...

272
00:21:44.770 --> 00:21:46.700
the 300 million dollar slush fund at C&T...

273
00:21:47.270 --> 00:21:50.370
and why our company.
Choiseong. is suffering all the fallout.

274
00:21:52.780 --> 00:21:54.280
I will launch a full-scale investigation...

275
00:21:54.350 --> 00:21:56.250
from an internal audit to
involving the prosecution.

276
00:22:00.550 --> 00:22:01.850
And by all means. suspect me as well.

277
00:22:02.790 --> 00:22:05.690
Kang Jae Seong. Jo Seon Hee.
Kang Bang Geul. and Lee Sang Jae.

278
00:22:06.560 --> 00:22:09.190
None of us are above
suspicion in this slush fund case.

279
00:22:09.530 --> 00:22:10.760
If I...

280
00:22:11.830 --> 00:22:13.800
have anything to do with
even a single penny of it.

281
00:22:14.330 --> 00:22:15.929
I will resign as president of Chemical.

282
00:22:15.930 --> 00:22:16.970
and I will not inherit...

283
00:22:17.640 --> 00:22:19.400
a single cent.

284
00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:22.510
Because that would mean I'm
not qualified to lead Choiseong.

285
00:22:24.910 --> 00:22:27.280
I will stake my entire
reputation on this...

286
00:22:27.880 --> 00:22:29.880
and root out the source of this corruption.

287
00:22:31.720 --> 00:22:33.380
What about the CCTV
footage from Father's ward?

288
00:22:33.620 --> 00:22:35.150
We're handling it as you instructed.

289
00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:40.090
Professor Min has apparently
resigned from the hospital.

290
00:22:42.030 --> 00:22:43.460
Where is he now?

291
00:22:45.030 --> 00:22:47.330
Don't tell me you're the one who
put a camera in my father's room...

292
00:22:59.980 --> 00:23:01.350
Why are you back so early?

293
00:23:02.110 --> 00:23:03.880
I thought you'd be swamped
dealing with everything.

294
00:23:05.320 --> 00:23:06.380
What is all this?

295
00:23:06.680 --> 00:23:07.690
No.

296
00:23:08.090 --> 00:23:09.519
Why did you resign from the hospital?

297
00:23:09.520 --> 00:23:11.560
We agreed you were
going to take a sabbatical.

298
00:23:12.460 --> 00:23:14.260
Well. I've been thinking.

299
00:23:14.960 --> 00:23:16.530
and I've decided there's no need for that.

300
00:23:17.560 --> 00:23:18.560
- What?
- I'll be...

301
00:23:18.630 --> 00:23:20.870
the husband of Choiseong's
chairwoman from now on.

302
00:23:21.570 --> 00:23:23.070
I've earned that much. haven't I?

303
00:23:24.100 --> 00:23:25.400
In fact. I feel relieved.

304
00:23:27.470 --> 00:23:29.810
Code Blue in Neurosurgery.

305
00:23:30.140 --> 00:23:34.710
All Neurosurgery staff
report to the VIP Ward ICU.

306
00:23:35.810 --> 00:23:36.980
Defibrillator. now.

307
00:23:39.280 --> 00:23:40.350
Clear.

308
00:23:42.350 --> 00:23:43.390
Charge to 200.

309
00:23:45.490 --> 00:23:46.690
Get the ECMO ready. now.

310
00:23:48.830 --> 00:23:51.200
I've really done everything I could.

311
00:23:56.500 --> 00:23:57.500
Congratulations. honey.

312
00:23:58.370 --> 00:24:00.170
Everything turned out
just the way you wanted.

313
00:24:01.570 --> 00:24:03.310
All that's left for our
family is to be happy.

314
00:24:09.750 --> 00:24:10.780
Do you really mean that?

315
00:24:14.920 --> 00:24:15.920
Of course.

316
00:24:17.820 --> 00:24:19.490
Your father's funeral
procession hasn't even started.

317
00:24:19.560 --> 00:24:20.560
We need to be careful.

318
00:24:21.160 --> 00:24:23.290
We can't afford any scandals
with such good things ahead of us.

319
00:24:34.270 --> 00:24:36.110
- Good work. sir.
- Take me to the funeral hall.

320
00:24:36.140 --> 00:24:37.170
You can't. sir.

321
00:24:37.240 --> 00:24:39.980
I have to check on Ms. Jo. She
must not be in her right mind.

322
00:24:40.040 --> 00:24:41.810
But Hwang Jun Hyeon
specifically told me that...

323
00:24:41.880 --> 00:24:44.620
you shouldn't be allowed
anywhere near the funeral hall.

324
00:24:45.920 --> 00:24:49.350
He said you need to stand
against Chairman Kang now.

325
00:24:49.820 --> 00:24:51.060
Otherwise. all the
trouble you went through...

326
00:24:51.560 --> 00:24:54.760
to testify against Chairman
Kang could be for nothing.

327
00:24:56.630 --> 00:24:58.460
But how could you not go? Right?

328
00:24:58.530 --> 00:25:00.760
Let's just go. I'll make
sure you're not seen.

329
00:25:01.370 --> 00:25:02.730
Do as Hwang Jun Hyeon says.

330
00:25:04.540 --> 00:25:06.040
The one who's having
the hardest time right now...

331
00:25:07.270 --> 00:25:08.470
is him.

332
00:25:21.450 --> 00:25:22.690
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

333
00:25:37.300 --> 00:25:40.070
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

334
00:25:45.240 --> 00:25:46.840
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

335
00:25:57.890 --> 00:25:59.060
Why are you lying down?

336
00:26:01.890 --> 00:26:03.630
You said you'd fight to the end.

337
00:26:04.630 --> 00:26:06.560
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

338
00:26:12.270 --> 00:26:13.400
(The Late Hwang Jun Hyeon)

339
00:26:15.440 --> 00:26:18.540
You still have to get an apology
from them for ruining your life.

340
00:26:19.740 --> 00:26:20.740
Why...

341
00:26:34.290 --> 00:26:38.100
(The Late Hwang Jun Hyeon)

342
00:26:39.230 --> 00:26:40.660
Even knowing my own children...

343
00:26:42.470 --> 00:26:45.170
had tried to kill you.

344
00:26:47.740 --> 00:26:49.170
my selfish desire to fix...

345
00:26:49.910 --> 00:26:51.840
my broken life...

346
00:26:54.240 --> 00:26:56.050
made me turn a blind eye to you.

347
00:26:56.150 --> 00:26:59.150
(The Late Hwang Jun Hyeon)

348
00:27:03.490 --> 00:27:06.660
I was so blinded by my
need to protect Choiseong...

349
00:27:09.160 --> 00:27:11.560
that I let you end up in this state.

350
00:27:14.060 --> 00:27:15.330
As a father...

351
00:27:16.300 --> 00:27:19.340
and as a man. I have failed.

352
00:27:22.240 --> 00:27:23.970
Because of a man like me.

353
00:27:28.310 --> 00:27:29.880
you ended up dead.

354
00:27:32.120 --> 00:27:34.080
I'm so sorry.

355
00:27:35.020 --> 00:27:36.020
I am...

356
00:27:37.220 --> 00:27:38.290
so...

357
00:27:39.790 --> 00:27:41.160
sorry.

358
00:27:41.930 --> 00:27:43.660
I'm so sorry.

359
00:27:43.730 --> 00:27:46.230
(The Late Hwang Jun Hyeon)

360
00:28:04.680 --> 00:28:06.880
I'm going to set everything right.

361
00:28:07.550 --> 00:28:10.150
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

362
00:28:11.590 --> 00:28:12.890
Your grandmother...

363
00:28:19.530 --> 00:28:21.000
Don't you worry about her.

364
00:28:39.220 --> 00:28:40.780
Let's live here from now on.

365
00:28:42.120 --> 00:28:44.390
Don't trouble yourself
with cooking or cleaning.

366
00:28:45.520 --> 00:28:48.430
From now on. just order whatever
you need to be delivered here.

367
00:28:51.160 --> 00:28:52.160
What about my boy?

368
00:28:55.100 --> 00:28:56.400
Where's my Jun Hyeon?

369
00:28:57.370 --> 00:28:58.500
Jun Hyeon!

370
00:29:00.100 --> 00:29:02.510
Jun Hyeon. Where's Jun Hyeon?

371
00:29:02.810 --> 00:29:03.810
Jun Hyeon.

372
00:29:04.510 --> 00:29:06.940
Jun Hyeon.

373
00:29:06.980 --> 00:29:08.610
Where did he go?

374
00:29:10.180 --> 00:29:11.980
Where are you? Jun Hyeon!

375
00:29:13.020 --> 00:29:15.590
Jun Hyeon. Oh. where is my boy?

376
00:29:16.690 --> 00:29:19.260
- Jun Hyeon. Where are you?
- Snap out of it. okay?

377
00:29:20.420 --> 00:29:22.330
Just relax and live here.

378
00:29:26.300 --> 00:29:27.560
I want to go home.

379
00:29:31.770 --> 00:29:33.300
Take me to Jun Hyeon.

380
00:29:38.480 --> 00:29:39.480
All right. then.

381
00:29:41.280 --> 00:29:43.810
Let's go to Aejeong-dong. Ok Sun.

382
00:30:05.340 --> 00:30:06.470
How pretty.

383
00:30:08.470 --> 00:30:10.540
Come on. have a seat.
I'll take your picture.

384
00:30:10.610 --> 00:30:11.740
Sit down.

385
00:30:21.820 --> 00:30:25.620
- He's my grandson.
- Oh. he's so handsome. My goodness.

386
00:30:25.720 --> 00:30:26.990
Look who it is.

387
00:30:27.290 --> 00:30:29.730
It's been too long. You
should stop by more often.

388
00:30:31.460 --> 00:30:32.630
Thank you.

389
00:30:33.630 --> 00:30:35.170
Four are on the house. okay?

390
00:30:35.870 --> 00:30:36.870
Four of them.

391
00:30:51.050 --> 00:30:53.680
This is a first for me.

392
00:30:55.890 --> 00:30:58.320
- Enjoy your meal.
- I said we should eat at home.

393
00:30:58.560 --> 00:31:00.260
Especially after we
bought all these groceries.

394
00:31:00.320 --> 00:31:02.059
Come on. take a break.

395
00:31:02.060 --> 00:31:03.660
It must be exhausting cooking every meal.

396
00:31:03.790 --> 00:31:06.230
What's so hard about feeding my sweet boy?

397
00:31:07.200 --> 00:31:08.470
It's what brings me joy.

398
00:31:09.870 --> 00:31:12.100
And treating you is what
brings me joy. Ok Sun.

399
00:31:13.840 --> 00:31:15.570
I tried this before.

400
00:31:15.910 --> 00:31:17.570
and it was so good I
couldn't stop thinking about it.

401
00:31:17.940 --> 00:31:18.940
Here.

402
00:31:20.040 --> 00:31:21.040
Wrap it like this.

403
00:31:25.380 --> 00:31:27.520
It's delicious. Nice and spicy.

404
00:31:28.220 --> 00:31:29.220
Go on. you eat too.

405
00:31:38.160 --> 00:31:40.660
- Starting to clean.
- Gosh. this thing.

406
00:31:53.740 --> 00:31:55.879
This is for osteoporosis.

407
00:31:55.880 --> 00:31:58.080
Take one pill twice a
day. morning and evening.

408
00:31:59.280 --> 00:32:02.790
This is for diabetes. Since
your fasting sugar is high.

409
00:32:02.850 --> 00:32:05.020
take one pill in the evening.
And this is for your blood pressure.

410
00:32:05.120 --> 00:32:07.990
- As soon as you get up...
- I'll be full from these pills.

411
00:32:08.330 --> 00:32:09.890
What am I. some critical patient?

412
00:32:10.230 --> 00:32:13.260
From now on... What's that saying?

413
00:32:14.330 --> 00:32:16.700
You'll have nothing but
good things ahead of you.

414
00:32:18.840 --> 00:32:19.840
My sweet boy.

415
00:32:20.770 --> 00:32:21.770
Is something wrong?

416
00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.610
(Kang Bang Geul)

417
00:32:30.710 --> 00:32:33.120
It's been ringing for a
while. You should answer it.

418
00:32:33.920 --> 00:32:34.920
Okay.

419
00:32:36.820 --> 00:32:37.820
Hello.

420
00:32:55.210 --> 00:32:56.210
Dad.

421
00:32:59.240 --> 00:33:01.510
Why did you leave so
soon without even letting...

422
00:33:01.580 --> 00:33:04.110
your youngest daughter
treat you to a bowl of soup?

423
00:33:06.380 --> 00:33:08.720
I wanted you to pour me...

424
00:33:09.720 --> 00:33:11.790
a glass of soju.

425
00:33:16.160 --> 00:33:18.930
You never even once looked
at my face with affection.

426
00:33:21.700 --> 00:33:24.330
You never even spoke to me first.

427
00:33:30.140 --> 00:33:33.540
I'm doing just as well
as my brother and sister.

428
00:33:38.580 --> 00:33:40.880
I'm all grown up now and can hold my own.

429
00:33:45.390 --> 00:33:48.560
so I came back. hoping
you would finally notice me.

430
00:33:52.100 --> 00:33:54.300
Why did you have to go so soon?

431
00:33:55.130 --> 00:33:56.130
Why?

432
00:34:05.140 --> 00:34:06.440
Dad.

433
00:34:11.210 --> 00:34:12.650
Dad.

434
00:34:19.760 --> 00:34:22.960
Don't ever cry because
of your father again.

435
00:34:25.060 --> 00:34:27.200
I'm sorry. Bang Geul.

436
00:34:33.640 --> 00:34:35.510
Who gave you the right to cremate him?

437
00:34:36.510 --> 00:34:37.840
I never agreed to it!

438
00:34:38.110 --> 00:34:39.110
I did.

439
00:34:39.940 --> 00:34:41.880
Isn't it enough that the eldest son agreed?

440
00:34:42.550 --> 00:34:44.050
Why are outsiders butting in?

441
00:34:44.780 --> 00:34:48.550
Mom is legally Dad's
wife. and I'm his daughter.

442
00:34:48.790 --> 00:34:49.790
What are you so guilty about...

443
00:34:49.850 --> 00:34:51.090
that you had him
cremated without telling us?

444
00:34:51.350 --> 00:34:54.060
What is there to feel guilty
about? Just like Seok Do said.

445
00:34:54.360 --> 00:34:56.690
didn't Father pass away from
being in a long-term coma?

446
00:34:56.830 --> 00:34:58.960
She suspects that I killed him.

447
00:34:59.430 --> 00:35:01.500
Under the pretext of performing
an autopsy on our father's body.

448
00:35:02.070 --> 00:35:04.430
- she wanted to knife him.
- Jae Gyeong!

449
00:35:04.500 --> 00:35:06.800
That's enough. Not in front of the kids.

450
00:35:08.910 --> 00:35:09.910
Attorney Yang.

451
00:35:10.370 --> 00:35:12.440
Please proceed with
the reading of the will.

452
00:35:14.640 --> 00:35:15.650
Then. I will now...

453
00:35:16.380 --> 00:35:17.980
read the will of Chairman Kang Yong Ho...

454
00:35:19.120 --> 00:35:20.150
out loud.

455
00:35:20.820 --> 00:35:23.220
The building in Nonhyeon-dong
and the land in Pangyo. Bundang...

456
00:35:23.290 --> 00:35:24.590
previously owned by the Chairman...

457
00:35:24.820 --> 00:35:26.190
are bequeathed to his wife. Jo Seon Hee.

458
00:35:26.860 --> 00:35:29.230
To his eldest son. Kang Jae Seong.
the buildings in Cheongdam-dong...

459
00:35:29.290 --> 00:35:31.460
and Yangjae-dong. and the
Choiseong property on Jeju.

460
00:35:31.700 --> 00:35:33.060
To his eldest daughter. Kang Jae Gyeong.

461
00:35:33.130 --> 00:35:35.330
the building in Samseong-dong.
the residence in Pyeongchang-dong.

462
00:35:35.500 --> 00:35:36.600
and the vacation home in Hawaii.

463
00:35:36.900 --> 00:35:39.440
To second daughter. Kang Bang
Geul. the building in Sinsa-dong...

464
00:35:39.500 --> 00:35:41.840
and the New York building. To
his daughter-in-law. Na Eun Se.

465
00:35:42.210 --> 00:35:44.740
the building in Seongbuk-dong
and the vacation home in Miami.

466
00:35:45.310 --> 00:35:46.810
To his son-in-law. Min Seok Do.

467
00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:48.880
the golf course and resort in Yangpyeong.

468
00:35:49.180 --> 00:35:52.680
And to his grandchildren.
Min Il Jun and Kang I Jun.

469
00:35:53.080 --> 00:35:56.820
he bequeaths one percent of
Choiseong Group's shares to each.

470
00:35:56.990 --> 00:35:58.760
All other assets...

471
00:35:59.020 --> 00:36:00.860
will be inherited by the next chairman.

472
00:36:01.020 --> 00:36:02.960
So I guess no one is his child
except for the next chairman?

473
00:36:04.260 --> 00:36:06.230
And on top of that. he gives all
the prime assets to an outsider.

474
00:36:06.660 --> 00:36:07.660
Congratulations.

475
00:36:08.370 --> 00:36:10.130
You really got yourself a
hefty severance package.

476
00:36:10.300 --> 00:36:11.300
Watch your mouth.

477
00:36:13.040 --> 00:36:15.640
I wonder if she'll have time
to accept any congratulations.

478
00:36:18.040 --> 00:36:20.340
Ms. Jo Seon Hee. We're
from the Prosecutor's Office.

479
00:36:20.680 --> 00:36:21.950
You'll have to come with
us regarding the charges...

480
00:36:22.010 --> 00:36:23.310
related to Choiseong C&T's slush fund.

481
00:36:25.580 --> 00:36:26.580
Mom.

482
00:36:28.690 --> 00:36:29.890
A slush fund?

483
00:36:30.450 --> 00:36:31.590
What are you talking about?

484
00:36:31.760 --> 00:36:33.320
We have evidence
suggesting you were involved...

485
00:36:33.390 --> 00:36:34.760
in managing Chairman Kang's slush fund.

486
00:36:35.030 --> 00:36:36.760
We're executing an arrest warrant.

487
00:36:37.190 --> 00:36:38.900
Ms. Jo Seon Hee. you
have the right to remain silent.

488
00:36:38.960 --> 00:36:41.230
Any statement you make can
be used against you in court.

489
00:36:42.900 --> 00:36:46.140
Wait. This has to be a
mistake! This is all a mistake.

490
00:36:46.370 --> 00:36:47.940
Mom. what is...

491
00:36:48.440 --> 00:36:49.440
It's all right.

492
00:36:52.310 --> 00:36:54.980
If she's innocent. she'll
be out soon. just like I was.

493
00:36:55.250 --> 00:36:56.750
What are you worried about?

494
00:37:02.990 --> 00:37:04.790
So this is how you're
making me pay you back?

495
00:37:05.120 --> 00:37:07.260
You have to pay the price
for selling out our father.

496
00:37:08.290 --> 00:37:09.530
You should start looking for a lawyer.

497
00:37:09.960 --> 00:37:12.700
Oh. but you probably have no money.

498
00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:14.860
Because your assets. your mother's.

499
00:37:14.930 --> 00:37:17.330
and the inheritance from
our father will all be seized.

500
00:37:18.840 --> 00:37:20.470
To pay back the slush fund.

501
00:37:20.600 --> 00:37:23.170
You fabricated all of this. It's all fake!

502
00:37:23.240 --> 00:37:25.440
Weren't you and your mother
the fake ones from the start?

503
00:37:26.580 --> 00:37:30.280
- We were never a real family.
- Hey. Kang Jae Gyeong!

504
00:37:30.350 --> 00:37:34.420
How dare you say your
sister's name like that?

505
00:37:34.580 --> 00:37:36.450
I should be the one glaring here.

506
00:37:37.350 --> 00:37:39.560
Being associated with you has
brought me nothing but bad luck.

507
00:37:39.790 --> 00:37:42.490
So stop stalling and get out of here!

508
00:37:44.390 --> 00:37:45.400
Fine.

509
00:37:47.730 --> 00:37:48.930
Once an outcast.

510
00:37:50.730 --> 00:37:51.940
always an outcast.

511
00:37:52.670 --> 00:37:56.270
I'll remove this lifelong
burden from your lives.

512
00:37:56.740 --> 00:37:59.340
so you can all enjoy living
miserably in this house.

513
00:38:03.880 --> 00:38:05.450
Unbelievable. She's rude to the very end.

514
00:38:07.450 --> 00:38:09.690
Good riddance.

515
00:38:11.790 --> 00:38:15.020
Do you want to be my
big sister. while we're at it?

516
00:38:19.930 --> 00:38:21.030
During the investigation.

517
00:38:21.830 --> 00:38:23.300
your personal assets. Ms. Jo. as well as...

518
00:38:23.700 --> 00:38:26.600
the inheritance you received from
Mr. Kang Yong Ho. will be seized.

519
00:38:26.840 --> 00:38:29.110
If you're found guilty.
it will all be confiscated.

520
00:38:29.410 --> 00:38:30.410
Take it all.

521
00:38:31.980 --> 00:38:33.780
I don't need any of that.

522
00:38:34.040 --> 00:38:37.310
The slush fund from Kang
Yong Ho funnelled to you.

523
00:38:38.650 --> 00:38:39.850
Are you admitting to that?

524
00:38:40.250 --> 00:38:41.250
Yes.

525
00:38:42.850 --> 00:38:44.420
I did it. All of it.

526
00:38:45.460 --> 00:38:47.390
My husband is completely innocent.

527
00:38:48.590 --> 00:38:52.930
I'm the one who siphoned
all that money. So. lock me up.

528
00:38:53.660 --> 00:38:55.030
Arrest me.

529
00:38:59.800 --> 00:39:00.900
My mom's personal seal...

530
00:39:02.240 --> 00:39:04.840
and bankbook are missing. I
think Kang Jae Gyeong took them.

531
00:39:05.180 --> 00:39:06.680
What should I do. Mr. Lee?

532
00:39:07.110 --> 00:39:09.079
I'm on my way to the prosecutor's
office with the legal team now.

533
00:39:09.080 --> 00:39:10.580
Don't worry too much.

534
00:39:11.310 --> 00:39:12.320
Thank you.

535
00:39:13.350 --> 00:39:14.350
Please call me.

536
00:39:16.820 --> 00:39:18.990
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

537
00:39:23.690 --> 00:39:24.790
The person you are calling is unavailable.

538
00:39:24.860 --> 00:39:25.860
Please leave a message after the tone.

539
00:39:26.060 --> 00:39:27.800
Why isn't he answering his phone?

540
00:39:36.470 --> 00:39:39.680
Let my mom go right now. Or
else you and Kang Jae Gyeong...

541
00:39:40.080 --> 00:39:42.010
Be quiet. Someone will hear you.

542
00:39:42.910 --> 00:39:45.920
That crazy witch Kang Jae
Gyeong has gone way too far.

543
00:39:46.250 --> 00:39:47.520
Your mom and a slush fund?

544
00:39:47.880 --> 00:39:49.750
The woman spent her whole life
walking on eggshells around us.

545
00:39:49.820 --> 00:39:51.450
She couldn't even pretend
to be the wife of a chaebol.

546
00:39:51.590 --> 00:39:52.590
There's no way.

547
00:39:54.720 --> 00:39:55.960
What's your game right now?

548
00:40:03.670 --> 00:40:06.240
I'm a better actor than you think.

549
00:40:06.740 --> 00:40:07.740
Kang Bang Geul.

550
00:40:08.940 --> 00:40:09.940
I'm sorry.

551
00:40:11.170 --> 00:40:13.109
I know. You're probably thinking...

552
00:40:13.110 --> 00:40:14.710
"What kind of crazy act
is this jerk pulling now?"

553
00:40:14.940 --> 00:40:18.550
But this is the only way I can
fool that cunning witch Jae Gyeong.

554
00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:22.790
You think I'm going to fall for it again?

555
00:40:23.920 --> 00:40:24.920
I'm serious.

556
00:40:25.460 --> 00:40:26.990
I swore before our father.

557
00:40:28.060 --> 00:40:30.630
From now on. you. Kang
Bang Geul. are my only sister.

558
00:40:31.390 --> 00:40:33.900
And that I'll finally start
acting like a proper big brother.

559
00:40:34.260 --> 00:40:38.169
I'll make Kang Jae Gyeong kneel to you.

560
00:40:38.170 --> 00:40:39.170
No!

561
00:40:39.740 --> 00:40:41.269
I'll be the one to make
Kang Jae Gyeong kneel...

562
00:40:41.270 --> 00:40:43.270
before our father's grave. And you too.

563
00:40:44.770 --> 00:40:45.780
Fine.

564
00:40:46.340 --> 00:40:47.680
Of course I'll be punished.

565
00:40:48.210 --> 00:40:51.380
After I find out what kind of deal
Kang Jae Gyeong and Taeha made.

566
00:40:53.620 --> 00:40:56.090
You also sensed something
was off between those two. right?

567
00:40:57.720 --> 00:40:58.860
Just trust me.

568
00:41:00.060 --> 00:41:02.990
So. I'm going to act pretty
harsh in front of others.

569
00:41:04.490 --> 00:41:06.659
- What?
- Contempt and disdain...

570
00:41:06.660 --> 00:41:08.430
will be the norm. along
with scorn and belittlement.

571
00:41:08.600 --> 00:41:12.440
I'll stick to Kang Jae Gyeong's
side like a leech and torment you.

572
00:41:13.300 --> 00:41:16.410
Because you have to
fool yourself to fool others.

573
00:41:16.470 --> 00:41:18.040
It's a form of mind control.

574
00:41:18.840 --> 00:41:19.840
You understand. right?

575
00:41:19.910 --> 00:41:23.380
That's a grand way of saying
you'll just act like you always do.

576
00:41:23.510 --> 00:41:24.680
Just as I thought.

577
00:41:25.620 --> 00:41:27.520
Bang Geul. you're a tough one.

578
00:41:28.050 --> 00:41:29.050
I like that attitude.

579
00:41:37.290 --> 00:41:38.330
Use this to find a place.

580
00:41:38.760 --> 00:41:40.800
It'll be safer for you in
many ways if you move out.

581
00:41:43.700 --> 00:41:45.470
Okay. enough of the sentimental stuff.

582
00:41:47.200 --> 00:41:50.270
Kang Jae Gyeong will be inaugurated
as the new chairwoman today.

583
00:41:50.710 --> 00:41:53.610
- What are you talking about?
- They called an emergency meeting.

584
00:41:54.610 --> 00:41:55.610
In the middle of the night?

585
00:41:55.710 --> 00:41:56.780
(2026 Emergency Board of Directors Meeting)

586
00:41:56.850 --> 00:41:58.450
(Agenda: Appointment and
Inauguration of the Chairwoman)

587
00:42:14.830 --> 00:42:15.830
Please. have a seat.

588
00:42:16.330 --> 00:42:17.670
I look forward to your continued support.

589
00:42:17.870 --> 00:42:19.800
Likewise. I'm counting on you all.

590
00:42:26.880 --> 00:42:28.540
It's all just a prearranged formality.

591
00:42:28.850 --> 00:42:30.680
The outcome has already been decided.

592
00:42:46.400 --> 00:42:47.530
From now on.

593
00:42:49.100 --> 00:42:50.630
it's going to be Kang Jae Gyeong's world.

594
00:43:00.340 --> 00:43:01.980
(Kang Jae Seong. Hyeon Jin)

595
00:43:03.480 --> 00:43:06.150
So that you won't have a
single regret about your choice.

596
00:43:07.080 --> 00:43:08.580
I will lead Choiseong.

597
00:43:14.920 --> 00:43:17.590
Please join me.

598
00:43:20.600 --> 00:43:21.600
(Donghae Heavy Industries)

599
00:43:21.660 --> 00:43:22.930
(Ministry of Trade. Industry and Energy)

600
00:43:23.000 --> 00:43:24.500
(Kim Do Hyeon. Donghae
Heavy Industries Chairman)

601
00:43:24.830 --> 00:43:26.900
(Inauguration of Kang Jae Gyeong.
3rd Chairman Of Choiseong Group)

602
00:43:29.010 --> 00:43:31.670
(Choiseong: Future Business Leader.
Kang Jae Gyeong. 3rd Chairwoman)

603
00:43:36.080 --> 00:43:39.180
The funeral was just a few days ago.

604
00:43:39.520 --> 00:43:40.950
And just like that. an
inauguration ceremony?

605
00:43:41.050 --> 00:43:44.290
It's like the entire universe is
conspiring to make her chairwoman.

606
00:43:44.350 --> 00:43:45.589
It's obviously part of...

607
00:43:45.590 --> 00:43:46.820
Kang Jae Gyeong's master plan. isn't it?

608
00:43:48.830 --> 00:43:49.830
What about Hwang Jun Hyeon?

609
00:43:50.130 --> 00:43:52.930
I stopped by his place on my way here.

610
00:43:53.330 --> 00:43:56.130
and they said he went to
work. But he isn't at the office.

611
00:43:57.300 --> 00:43:59.500
This means he's avoiding my calls. right?

612
00:44:00.340 --> 00:44:01.840
Did something really happen to him?

613
00:44:07.310 --> 00:44:08.610
Come on. let's go.

614
00:44:09.650 --> 00:44:12.050
What is it now? Goodness.

615
00:44:16.220 --> 00:44:17.450
Are you admitting to the
slush fund allegations...

616
00:44:17.520 --> 00:44:19.820
- at Choiseong C&T?
- Did you act alone?

617
00:44:19.920 --> 00:44:22.760
We just have to trust Managing
Director Lee and the legal team.

618
00:44:22.960 --> 00:44:25.460
- That's our only option.
- No.

619
00:44:28.000 --> 00:44:29.000
There is...

620
00:44:30.070 --> 00:44:31.330
a way to stop Kang Jae Gyeong.

621
00:44:45.820 --> 00:44:47.750
The Chairwoman is arriving.

622
00:44:50.150 --> 00:44:51.650
(Air Quality Index. Sunny)

623
00:45:30.660 --> 00:45:31.890
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

624
00:45:41.400 --> 00:45:45.340
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

625
00:45:45.710 --> 00:45:46.710
Chairwoman...

626
00:45:47.940 --> 00:45:49.080
Kang Jae Gyeong.

627
00:45:52.150 --> 00:45:55.080
Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong.

628
00:46:05.090 --> 00:46:06.300
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

629
00:46:09.070 --> 00:46:10.400
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

630
00:46:12.470 --> 00:46:14.470
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

631
00:46:20.110 --> 00:46:21.910
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

632
00:46:23.450 --> 00:46:26.150
You should've at least brought
flowers on a day like this.

633
00:46:27.080 --> 00:46:28.520
So rude. coming empty-handed...

634
00:46:29.890 --> 00:46:31.919
Oh. well. Since you're about to be jobless.

635
00:46:31.920 --> 00:46:33.390
you have to save every penny.

636
00:46:34.490 --> 00:46:37.590
Secretary Yeo. is the
inaugural oath ready yet?

637
00:46:37.890 --> 00:46:39.830
It's all prepared. Madam Chairwoman.

638
00:46:41.900 --> 00:46:42.900
I'll give them to you.

639
00:46:43.770 --> 00:46:45.670
The shares you want in Choiseong Solution.

640
00:46:47.200 --> 00:46:48.240
My 15 percent.

641
00:46:49.310 --> 00:46:50.340
I'll sign them all over.

642
00:46:51.140 --> 00:46:53.440
Promise you'll stop them from
arresting Mom and leave her alone.

643
00:46:53.610 --> 00:46:54.910
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

644
00:46:57.480 --> 00:47:00.380
So. you are a dutiful
daughter after all. Bang Geul.

645
00:47:01.450 --> 00:47:02.450
Just like someone said.

646
00:47:05.120 --> 00:47:07.420
(Transferor: Casey Kang)

647
00:47:09.190 --> 00:47:10.260
I'm sorry. Hwang Jun Hyeon.

648
00:47:10.590 --> 00:47:12.160
I had no choice. I have to save my mom.

649
00:47:15.930 --> 00:47:17.030
You'd better keep your promise.

650
00:47:23.370 --> 00:47:25.170
The arrest warrant will
be dismissed immediately.

651
00:47:26.410 --> 00:47:29.250
Are you staying for my
inauguration ceremony?

652
00:47:30.610 --> 00:47:33.420
I have to. You're the
Chairwoman I'll be serving now.

653
00:47:38.620 --> 00:47:40.920
I'm sure some will judge us...

654
00:47:41.860 --> 00:47:44.060
for our short period of mourning.

655
00:47:44.830 --> 00:47:47.000
I will accept all of that criticism.

656
00:47:47.830 --> 00:47:50.470
I will also be the one
who protects you all...

657
00:47:51.170 --> 00:47:52.300
and Choiseong.

658
00:47:53.070 --> 00:47:55.240
I will make sure you never
have to hang your heads...

659
00:47:55.300 --> 00:47:56.470
because of Choiseong again.

660
00:47:57.210 --> 00:47:59.010
Starting today. Choiseong changes.

661
00:47:59.380 --> 00:48:03.110
We desperately need
innovation. that something new.

662
00:48:04.050 --> 00:48:06.180
To create a blueprint
for all of Choiseong...

663
00:48:07.050 --> 00:48:10.290
and draw that future with
me. Kang Jae Gyeong.

664
00:48:11.690 --> 00:48:14.660
I am establishing the Future Business Team.

665
00:48:16.130 --> 00:48:19.860
Head of the Future Business
Team. Choiseong's new control tower.

666
00:48:23.470 --> 00:48:26.040
is Mr. Hwang Jun Hyeon.

667
00:48:36.310 --> 00:48:37.550
That crazy jerk.

668
00:48:37.610 --> 00:48:41.020
(Chairwoman Kang Jae
Gyeong's Inauguration Ceremony)

669
00:48:46.860 --> 00:48:47.990
Hello. everyone.

670
00:48:49.020 --> 00:48:51.030
I'm the head of the Future
Business Team at Choiseong Group.

671
00:48:51.460 --> 00:48:52.460
Hwang Jun Hyeon.

672
00:48:53.200 --> 00:48:54.230
I look forward to working with you all.

673
00:48:54.500 --> 00:48:55.500
(Chairwoman Kang Jae
Gyeong's Inauguration Ceremony)

674
00:49:10.180 --> 00:49:12.310
I'm not interested in
your surprises anymore.

675
00:49:13.050 --> 00:49:14.120
I know.

676
00:49:14.750 --> 00:49:16.550
That I've been overstepping
my bounds all this time.

677
00:49:16.890 --> 00:49:19.320
You said you'd never take my hand.

678
00:49:20.190 --> 00:49:21.920
What. are you trying to apologise now?

679
00:49:22.320 --> 00:49:25.230
Honestly. I wanted revenge for
you ruining my soccer career...

680
00:49:26.130 --> 00:49:28.000
by using Kang Bang Geul.

681
00:49:28.860 --> 00:49:31.030
But after Chairman Kang
died. I finally understood...

682
00:49:32.130 --> 00:49:35.040
what kind of person you
are and the power you hold.

683
00:49:35.700 --> 00:49:37.270
And that's what brought me here.

684
00:49:38.410 --> 00:49:40.080
I already have Choiseong.

685
00:49:40.840 --> 00:49:41.840
Too bad for you.

686
00:49:43.980 --> 00:49:45.250
I'll give you what you want.

687
00:49:50.890 --> 00:49:53.290
Half of Smile Investment's
shares in Choiseong Solution.

688
00:49:59.830 --> 00:50:03.600
My business partner
turned out to be quite lacking.

689
00:50:05.170 --> 00:50:06.170
(Kang Smile)

690
00:50:06.870 --> 00:50:09.370
I want a fresh start with
a competent partner.

691
00:50:11.110 --> 00:50:12.780
With this. I'm sure you must need me now.

692
00:50:13.540 --> 00:50:16.110
You're going to give me
Kang Bang Geul's shares?

693
00:50:18.480 --> 00:50:21.480
I need to have some skin
in the game to be motivated.

694
00:50:23.120 --> 00:50:24.989
and being tied by shares
will strengthen our partnership.

695
00:50:24.990 --> 00:50:26.420
Don't you think?

696
00:50:27.660 --> 00:50:30.360
How do you plan on getting the
shares from a vengeful Bang Geul?

697
00:50:31.630 --> 00:50:33.360
Let's use Ms. Jo Seon Hee.

698
00:50:35.060 --> 00:50:36.799
If you hit an opponent
where they're weakest.

699
00:50:36.800 --> 00:50:38.670
they'll get scared and cough it up.

700
00:50:43.910 --> 00:50:46.480
That's right. Trust me.

701
00:50:47.140 --> 00:50:49.850
Let's hit rock bottom together.

702
00:50:50.780 --> 00:50:51.850
Jae Gyeong.

703
00:50:53.580 --> 00:50:54.780
From now on. Choiseong...

704
00:50:55.320 --> 00:50:57.950
will make personnel decisions
based strictly on merit...

705
00:50:58.350 --> 00:51:01.490
and foster a new generation of Choiseong...

706
00:51:02.260 --> 00:51:05.260
where more people like
Hwang Jun Hyeon can emerge.

707
00:51:11.400 --> 00:51:14.100
Losing her key player must've
been a real shock for Kang Bang Geul.

708
00:51:16.840 --> 00:51:19.580
She's lucky she wasn't fired.

709
00:51:21.440 --> 00:51:22.440
Ms. Kang.

710
00:51:25.680 --> 00:51:26.680
Are you okay?

711
00:51:30.550 --> 00:51:32.390
Hwang Jun Hyeon... What...

712
00:51:33.490 --> 00:51:35.020
What is he plotting now?

713
00:51:38.660 --> 00:51:40.130
(Strategy and Planning Team)

714
00:51:41.300 --> 00:51:42.900
(Future Business Team)

715
00:51:49.940 --> 00:51:51.110
This is too cramped.

716
00:51:51.740 --> 00:51:53.180
I told you to take the office next to mine.

717
00:51:53.780 --> 00:51:55.610
But isn't it more fun to work your way up?

718
00:51:56.350 --> 00:51:57.380
This is perfect.

719
00:51:58.480 --> 00:52:00.780
Team Leader Jo from the Audit
Team will join you right away.

720
00:52:01.080 --> 00:52:02.450
and I'll leave the rest of the staffing...

721
00:52:02.520 --> 00:52:03.890
to your discretion. Team Leader Hwang.

722
00:52:11.460 --> 00:52:12.490
Explain.

723
00:52:13.230 --> 00:52:16.470
Explain what this darn
situation is so I can understand.

724
00:52:16.930 --> 00:52:18.200
What's there to understand?

725
00:52:19.570 --> 00:52:20.700
It's exactly as it looks.

726
00:52:22.100 --> 00:52:24.310
Right. You must be shocked too.

727
00:52:25.110 --> 00:52:26.640
You must feel terribly sorry for me.

728
00:52:27.940 --> 00:52:30.180
But still. how could you do this to me?

729
00:52:30.250 --> 00:52:31.250
What's between us?

730
00:52:33.050 --> 00:52:35.220
- What?
- Whatever decisions I make.

731
00:52:35.650 --> 00:52:37.190
whoever I work for...

732
00:52:37.990 --> 00:52:39.720
What does that have to do with you?

733
00:52:40.960 --> 00:52:41.960
"You"?

734
00:52:42.320 --> 00:52:44.630
Is this pathetic display what you've
been working toward this whole time?

735
00:52:45.030 --> 00:52:47.259
What about the promise you made
me? You said you'd protect Choiseong.

736
00:52:47.260 --> 00:52:48.960
You said you'd prove my dad's innocence.

737
00:52:49.800 --> 00:52:52.200
You know my sister killed my dad!

738
00:52:53.200 --> 00:52:55.270
You can't just make
accusations without proof.

739
00:52:59.010 --> 00:53:03.580
Do I look stupid enough to go
down with you on a sinking ship?

740
00:53:05.880 --> 00:53:08.220
What someone like me
with a bright future needs...

741
00:53:09.280 --> 00:53:12.090
is a capable partner who can pull me up.

742
00:53:17.160 --> 00:53:18.660
You must not have heard yet.

743
00:53:19.430 --> 00:53:21.360
but your team was transferred
to another department...

744
00:53:21.430 --> 00:53:22.900
with Managing Director Lee. So pack up.

745
00:53:24.470 --> 00:53:26.740
And it'd be even better if you just
left Choiseong while you're at it.

746
00:53:28.900 --> 00:53:30.340
Shall we start the meeting. Chairwoman?

747
00:53:33.180 --> 00:53:35.840
So. you are a dutiful
daughter after all. Bang Geul.

748
00:53:36.980 --> 00:53:37.980
Just like someone said.

749
00:53:41.420 --> 00:53:44.150
Don't tell me you made
me give up my shares.

750
00:53:45.320 --> 00:53:47.420
Were you the one who had my mom arrested?

751
00:53:50.030 --> 00:53:51.190
Don't blame me.

752
00:53:53.130 --> 00:53:55.500
You're the one who was
too weak to protect her.

753
00:54:01.940 --> 00:54:03.270
(Future Business Team)

754
00:54:08.780 --> 00:54:10.180
Fine. go.

755
00:54:10.810 --> 00:54:12.920
Who said I'd be scared without you?

756
00:54:15.350 --> 00:54:16.420
Why should I leave?

757
00:54:17.650 --> 00:54:19.420
I'll fight tooth and nail to stay here.

758
00:54:19.790 --> 00:54:23.760
I'll latch on and never let go. I'm
going to watch you all go down!

759
00:54:27.460 --> 00:54:29.160
Aren't you overdoing
it just for my benefit?

760
00:54:30.000 --> 00:54:31.270
Let's be mindful of your public image...

761
00:54:31.330 --> 00:54:32.330
and pick our moments carefully.

762
00:54:32.940 --> 00:54:34.040
She won't last long.

763
00:54:34.540 --> 00:54:37.010
You know Kang Bang Geul.

764
00:54:39.410 --> 00:54:41.910
You probably know Kang Bang Geul
better than I do. Team Leader Hwang.

765
00:54:42.910 --> 00:54:44.680
Thanks to you. that mother and daughter...

766
00:54:45.010 --> 00:54:46.680
are about to cough up
everything. including the penalty.

767
00:54:47.120 --> 00:54:50.020
They'll be kicked out penniless.
so I guess your wish came true.

768
00:54:51.550 --> 00:54:52.590
How did you know...

769
00:54:53.620 --> 00:54:54.690
that that was my wish?

770
00:55:02.900 --> 00:55:04.470
(Notice: Abolition of Strategy and Planning Team)

771
00:55:04.530 --> 00:55:06.100
(Personnel Order)

772
00:55:06.170 --> 00:55:09.300
{\an8}(Demotions: Lee Sang Jae.
Park Bong Gi. Kang Bang Geul)

773
00:55:25.750 --> 00:55:27.090
What is this? What's going on?

774
00:55:36.730 --> 00:55:37.800
This is it.

775
00:55:38.570 --> 00:55:40.300
I didn't know we had a
place like this in our company.

776
00:55:40.570 --> 00:55:42.910
(Company-wide Task Resource Management Team)

777
00:55:48.340 --> 00:55:49.610
They want us to work here?

778
00:55:50.310 --> 00:55:52.280
It's like a secret hideout. I like it.

779
00:56:03.930 --> 00:56:04.930
This is heavy.

780
00:56:12.570 --> 00:56:14.800
- Did you see that. Mr. Park?
- What?

781
00:56:15.700 --> 00:56:16.710
Should we give it a shake?

782
00:56:24.110 --> 00:56:25.750
- Here.
- Okay.

783
00:56:27.020 --> 00:56:28.380
I wonder if it likes cheese.

784
00:56:28.950 --> 00:56:30.590
Mice like cheese.

785
00:56:31.420 --> 00:56:32.420
They do?

786
00:56:33.290 --> 00:56:34.990
Trying to break my spirit
with something like this?

787
00:56:35.560 --> 00:56:37.560
In your dreams. Do you have any
idea what I've been through to survive?

788
00:56:41.900 --> 00:56:43.700
Let's see who comes out on top.

789
00:56:47.870 --> 00:56:49.870
This is Team Leader Hwang Jun Hyeon...

790
00:56:50.140 --> 00:56:52.370
of the Future Business
Team. Everyone. say hello.

791
00:56:52.440 --> 00:56:54.840
I look forward to working
with and learning from you all.

792
00:56:58.550 --> 00:56:59.780
In line with the commercialization...

793
00:56:59.850 --> 00:57:01.350
of Choiseong Solution's
all-solid-state battery.

794
00:57:01.420 --> 00:57:02.850
we will begin establishing a pipeline...

795
00:57:02.920 --> 00:57:05.950
for the battery research center.
We're also scheduling tests.

796
00:57:06.590 --> 00:57:09.490
From now on. on behalf of the Chairwoman.

797
00:57:09.760 --> 00:57:11.760
the Future Business
Team will be taking the lead.

798
00:57:11.830 --> 00:57:13.900
(R6 Research Wing Production Plant)

799
00:57:14.160 --> 00:57:16.500
Seeing it in person. it's a
shame to hand it over to Taeha.

800
00:57:17.870 --> 00:57:20.340
Madam Chairwoman. you've
made a truly difficult decision.

801
00:57:20.640 --> 00:57:23.010
What's the status of the handover?

802
00:57:23.240 --> 00:57:25.210
The takeover process for the
hydrogen production facility...

803
00:57:25.270 --> 00:57:26.680
has begun with Taeha Group.

804
00:57:27.410 --> 00:57:29.750
All that's left is transferring
this Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

805
00:57:30.410 --> 00:57:32.449
We can't just give
something this good away.

806
00:57:32.450 --> 00:57:34.820
Tighten security for the tech team staff.

807
00:57:35.020 --> 00:57:37.650
Access to files related to core
technology is already limited.

808
00:57:38.590 --> 00:57:39.920
The access codes for the security keys...

809
00:57:39.990 --> 00:57:41.760
also change constantly.
so you don't need to worry.

810
00:57:43.590 --> 00:57:45.060
How do you know that. Team Leader Hwang?

811
00:57:45.330 --> 00:57:46.530
I found out while getting up...

812
00:57:46.600 --> 00:57:47.630
to speed on Choiseong's main businesses.

813
00:57:48.360 --> 00:57:50.600
It was upgraded under
Chairman Kang Yong Ho's orders.

814
00:57:52.170 --> 00:57:53.800
Anyone watching would think...

815
00:57:53.870 --> 00:57:54.900
you do all the work around
here. Team Leader Hwang.

816
00:57:55.440 --> 00:57:56.440
Right?

817
00:57:56.740 --> 00:57:59.070
Exactly.

818
00:58:00.140 --> 00:58:01.940
Until the Daesan Hydrogen
Complex deal is finalized.

819
00:58:03.280 --> 00:58:04.480
I will take full responsibility.

820
00:58:04.910 --> 00:58:07.620
Aren't you getting a little ahead
of yourself right from the start?

821
00:58:08.020 --> 00:58:09.450
I can feel them staring daggers at my back.

822
00:58:09.650 --> 00:58:12.390
It's because you're exceeding all
expectations. Team Leader Hwang.

823
00:58:12.650 --> 00:58:13.960
It's a shame I'm the only
one who sees it. right?

824
00:58:14.490 --> 00:58:17.830
She's trying to surround me
with enemies to keep me in check.

825
00:58:18.190 --> 00:58:20.460
So she can easily cut
me loose if she needs to.

826
00:58:20.960 --> 00:58:23.700
She still doesn't trust me completely?

827
00:58:24.470 --> 00:58:25.470
Madam Chairwoman.

828
00:58:26.870 --> 00:58:27.900
You have a visitor.

829
00:58:39.880 --> 00:58:41.180
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

830
00:58:50.690 --> 00:58:52.130
What brings you all the way here?

831
00:58:52.590 --> 00:58:54.100
I couldn't attend
Chairman Kang's funeral...

832
00:58:54.160 --> 00:58:56.260
because of the unfortunate circumstances.

833
00:58:56.970 --> 00:58:58.970
but I had to congratulate
you on becoming Chairwoman.

834
00:59:00.600 --> 00:59:04.910
It's a 400-year-old juniper. I
specially requested a fine specimen.

835
00:59:06.740 --> 00:59:07.740
Yes. sir.

836
00:59:12.910 --> 00:59:13.950
(Congratulations From Taeha. Na Byeong Mo)

837
00:59:14.820 --> 00:59:16.520
Thank you. I'll take good care of it.

838
00:59:17.050 --> 00:59:18.350
It has an ancient beauty.

839
00:59:22.990 --> 00:59:24.460
A magnificent. lone old pine.

840
00:59:25.960 --> 00:59:29.060
Usually. people give a sapling
to symbolize growing together.

841
00:59:29.400 --> 00:59:31.230
Perhaps you mean for our
Chairwoman to be like this old pine...

842
00:59:31.400 --> 00:59:35.000
weathering the storms and trials
of time? What a profound meaning.

843
00:59:35.440 --> 00:59:38.340
You surprise me every time we meet.

844
00:59:39.310 --> 00:59:41.880
Have you two met before?

845
00:59:44.480 --> 00:59:46.620
I'm Hwang Jun Hyeon. Team
Leader of the Future Business Team.

846
00:59:48.980 --> 00:59:51.990
Why do you always use
dirty tactics in business?

847
00:59:52.850 --> 00:59:54.260
We'll see each other again soon.

848
00:59:54.660 --> 00:59:55.660
Chairman Na.

849
00:59:56.390 --> 00:59:58.430
You were just as arrogant back then.

850
00:59:58.660 --> 01:00:00.459
You used to play soccer only.

851
01:00:00.460 --> 01:00:02.400
From Kang Bang Geul to Kang Jae Gyeong?

852
01:00:02.600 --> 01:00:05.900
- You must have a strange talent.
- Oh. talent? Not at all.

853
01:00:06.400 --> 01:00:08.800
I'm just an ignoramus
with no business degrees.

854
01:00:09.270 --> 01:00:11.770
I just work hard. that's all.
Just like you. Chairman Na.

855
01:00:12.810 --> 01:00:14.780
You started with your fists on
the backstreets of Myeongdong.

856
01:00:14.840 --> 01:00:17.380
and now you're the respectable
head of a major corporation. aren't you?

857
01:00:17.780 --> 01:00:20.380
Since my own career started with my body.

858
01:00:20.550 --> 01:00:23.120
I'm always learning so
much from you. Chairman Na.

859
01:00:25.250 --> 01:00:27.260
Team Leader Hwang isn't very eloquent.

860
01:00:27.660 --> 01:00:29.120
Please don't take it the wrong way. sir.

861
01:00:29.760 --> 01:00:30.760
Oh. gosh.

862
01:00:31.290 --> 01:00:32.390
The hydrogen business project.

863
01:00:33.760 --> 01:00:36.300
Doesn't my son-in-law resent
you for handing it over to Taeha?

864
01:00:36.770 --> 01:00:37.870
Resent me? Of course not.

865
01:00:38.170 --> 01:00:39.329
He's just grateful he managed to keep...

866
01:00:39.330 --> 01:00:40.540
his position as president.

867
01:00:40.940 --> 01:00:42.599
He even greets me every morning.

868
01:00:42.600 --> 01:00:44.040
But...

869
01:00:44.510 --> 01:00:47.510
now that you're the Chairwoman.
your math has gotten a bit weak.

870
01:00:47.880 --> 01:00:51.350
You shouldn't still be holding onto
the Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

871
01:00:51.710 --> 01:00:53.080
From what I see. Taeha...

872
01:00:53.580 --> 01:00:55.720
hasn't paid the remaining
balance for the sale yet.

873
01:01:04.030 --> 01:01:05.560
And you still owe me my share.

874
01:01:07.030 --> 01:01:09.870
Out of the 300 million sale price.
100 million dollars is separate.

875
01:01:09.930 --> 01:01:11.600
Secretary Jo will wrap
it up nicely for you.

876
01:01:12.000 --> 01:01:13.900
I wonder if you haven't
finished wrapping it?

877
01:01:15.070 --> 01:01:17.810
Maybe you just don't
feel like giving me my gift.

878
01:01:28.650 --> 01:01:29.920
Surely you don't think...

879
01:01:30.320 --> 01:01:32.650
you got to that chair all by yourself?

880
01:01:44.800 --> 01:01:48.100
I don't recall letting just
anyone get a piece of the pie.

881
01:01:58.310 --> 01:01:59.410
I hope that you...

882
01:02:00.080 --> 01:02:03.080
stay in that chair for a long time.

883
01:02:03.450 --> 01:02:04.450
I mean it.

884
01:02:06.690 --> 01:02:07.720
Thank you.

885
01:02:11.090 --> 01:02:12.760
Allow me to see you out. Chairman.

886
01:02:31.350 --> 01:02:32.810
Seeing as how Kang Jae Gyeong hired him.

887
01:02:33.180 --> 01:02:34.820
he's no ordinary man. Father.

888
01:02:35.580 --> 01:02:36.590
Be careful.

889
01:02:37.450 --> 01:02:39.390
The nail that sticks out
gets hammered down.

890
01:02:40.660 --> 01:02:43.930
Do you still go to Yetgol at
the foot of Mount Bukhan?

891
01:02:44.860 --> 01:02:48.200
The pajeon there is to die for. isn't it?

892
01:02:48.360 --> 01:02:51.199
Are you digging into my past already?

893
01:02:51.200 --> 01:02:52.370
Goodness.

894
01:02:52.830 --> 01:02:56.200
I've served two masters. Why not a third?

895
01:03:02.140 --> 01:03:03.950
Feel free to contact me anytime.

896
01:03:04.310 --> 01:03:05.950
It's been a while since I've
seen the inside of Taeha.

897
01:03:24.870 --> 01:03:26.670
Ms. Jo was just released.

898
01:03:49.520 --> 01:03:50.560
Why would you do that?

899
01:03:51.430 --> 01:03:53.830
Letting Jae Gyeong get her hands
on the Smile Investment shares...

900
01:03:54.200 --> 01:03:55.360
and having Ms. Jo arrested.

901
01:03:55.430 --> 01:03:56.770
Bang Geul said it was all your doing.

902
01:03:57.770 --> 01:03:59.600
She is absolutely furious.

903
01:04:04.510 --> 01:04:06.880
I found all the money
from the Chairman's safe.

904
01:04:07.480 --> 01:04:10.650
It'll be more than enough to settle
down in the US for a few years.

905
01:04:11.450 --> 01:04:14.120
Send Bang Geul and her mom
to the US as soon as you can.

906
01:04:14.420 --> 01:04:18.350
She just got back to be near her father.

907
01:04:18.950 --> 01:04:20.360
and you want me to send her back to the US?

908
01:04:22.960 --> 01:04:23.960
I can't do it.

909
01:04:24.790 --> 01:04:25.890
And Bang Geul won't go either.

910
01:04:26.460 --> 01:04:28.900
I'm going to kick them out of Choiseong.

911
01:04:30.500 --> 01:04:32.170
so you take responsibility and take them.

912
01:04:32.800 --> 01:04:34.539
- Sir.
- They've found the camera...

913
01:04:34.540 --> 01:04:35.570
from my hospital room.

914
01:04:36.040 --> 01:04:37.870
so the two of them will
keep being suspected.

915
01:04:38.440 --> 01:04:40.880
There's no telling what
might happen if they stay here.

916
01:04:41.710 --> 01:04:43.710
She even killed her own father.

917
01:04:44.910 --> 01:04:46.350
Is there anything she wouldn't do?

918
01:04:51.250 --> 01:04:52.320
Where...

919
01:04:53.890 --> 01:04:54.960
are the two of them right now?

920
01:05:01.330 --> 01:05:03.160
They say it's more delicious this way. Mom.

921
01:05:05.370 --> 01:05:07.900
It's strange that Jae
Gyeong suddenly let me go.

922
01:05:11.010 --> 01:05:12.610
Are you sure nothing happened to you?

923
01:05:14.510 --> 01:05:18.280
- Did you promise her your life?
- No.

924
01:05:18.810 --> 01:05:21.980
I just threatened her. and
she backed down immediately.

925
01:05:25.250 --> 01:05:27.860
The trial will continue.
just without detention.

926
01:05:28.320 --> 01:05:29.960
We have to uncover everything before then.

927
01:05:30.260 --> 01:05:31.460
Dad's innocence...

928
01:05:32.230 --> 01:05:33.560
and Kang Jae Gyeong's crimes.

929
01:05:38.270 --> 01:05:40.300
Seok Do had a strange look on his face.

930
01:05:40.940 --> 01:05:43.940
I'm sure he knows something.

931
01:05:45.040 --> 01:05:47.240
Seok Do. my foot.

932
01:05:49.510 --> 01:05:52.350
We must have sikhye.

933
01:05:53.250 --> 01:05:54.650
Seriously.

934
01:06:00.420 --> 01:06:02.120
Wait here. I'll go buy some.

935
01:06:12.800 --> 01:06:15.300
What do you think you're doing.
sleeping in a place like this?

936
01:06:16.140 --> 01:06:17.570
How reckless of these women.

937
01:06:21.280 --> 01:06:23.450
She can't even sleep on hard surfaces.

938
01:06:29.120 --> 01:06:30.120
My wife...

939
01:06:39.230 --> 01:06:41.060
Just look at how pale she is.

940
01:06:59.180 --> 01:07:00.780
Hey. you pervert!

941
01:07:03.020 --> 01:07:04.150
Mom. are you okay?

942
01:07:05.090 --> 01:07:07.190
Some young punk with
nothing better to do. Hey!

943
01:07:07.860 --> 01:07:09.020
Hey. you darn pervert!

944
01:07:09.220 --> 01:07:11.360
Don't go. It's dangerous.

945
01:07:11.530 --> 01:07:13.290
Mom. a jerk like that needs
to be taught a harsh lesson.

946
01:07:14.500 --> 01:07:15.530
Then I'm going with you.

947
01:07:16.630 --> 01:07:18.300
From now on. do everything with me.

948
01:07:19.970 --> 01:07:20.970
No.

949
01:07:22.400 --> 01:07:26.670
Gosh. Ms. Jo. You must have
been quite a fighter back in the day.

950
01:07:26.940 --> 01:07:29.640
There's nothing I wouldn't
do to protect my child.

951
01:07:30.950 --> 01:07:33.310
Mom. don't worry.

952
01:07:34.150 --> 01:07:35.350
I absolutely will not get hurt.

953
01:07:36.280 --> 01:07:37.290
Never.

954
01:07:46.360 --> 01:07:47.860
Which neighbourhood do you like. Mom?

955
01:07:51.230 --> 01:07:52.230
How about this one?

956
01:07:53.100 --> 01:07:54.700
The rent's too expensive.

957
01:07:56.570 --> 01:07:57.640
Is there anything cheaper?

958
01:07:57.940 --> 01:07:59.110
Let me see.

959
01:08:04.450 --> 01:08:07.520
Actually. I have a place in mind.

960
01:08:23.360 --> 01:08:25.670
Kicking her own father in the back...

961
01:08:31.940 --> 01:08:33.070
What? Ok Sun.

962
01:08:33.880 --> 01:08:35.080
Don't tell me you cooked.

963
01:08:36.280 --> 01:08:38.050
I told you not to lift a finger.

964
01:08:38.580 --> 01:08:40.880
- Honestly.
- Hey. traitor.

965
01:08:52.390 --> 01:08:55.360
At least he knows his place.

966
01:08:55.760 --> 01:08:58.100
What's this? Why are
you coming out of there?

967
01:08:58.370 --> 01:08:59.370
I moved in.

968
01:09:00.000 --> 01:09:01.470
I got kicked out of my home.
thanks to a certain someone.

969
01:09:01.970 --> 01:09:05.440
I get that. but why did you move here?

970
01:09:06.310 --> 01:09:08.110
Aejeong-dong was the cheapest.

971
01:09:08.580 --> 01:09:11.580
The air is nice. and
the view is to die for.

972
01:09:14.080 --> 01:09:15.580
And there's someone
I'd like to kill here too.

973
01:09:19.490 --> 01:09:21.060
Sweetheart. come and eat.

974
01:09:22.720 --> 01:09:24.160
Okay. Grandma.

975
01:09:25.690 --> 01:09:27.630
Hey. get out of the way.

976
01:09:28.460 --> 01:09:29.460
What?

977
01:09:35.300 --> 01:09:36.300
Nice landing.

978
01:09:43.340 --> 01:09:45.180
Let's try to get along.

979
01:09:46.380 --> 01:09:47.580
my dear neighbour.

980
01:09:59.260 --> 01:10:02.200
(Reborn Rookie)

981
01:10:23.250 --> 01:10:24.989
{\an8}You all know what they call us. right?

982
01:10:24.990 --> 01:10:25.990
{\an8}Or the "Ex-Con Team" for short.

983
01:10:26.020 --> 01:10:28.159
{\an8}As promised. I'll make sure
to send them to the US...

984
01:10:28.160 --> 01:10:31.190
{\an8}- by the end of the month.
- It's not hard at all.

985
01:10:31.330 --> 01:10:34.130
{\an8}Rumours are flying that Kang
Jae Gyeong killed her father.

986
01:10:34.200 --> 01:10:37.030
{\an8}They said the CCTV stopped
recording due to a security check.

987
01:10:37.100 --> 01:10:38.470
{\an8}Where is this guy now?

988
01:10:38.530 --> 01:10:41.270
{\an8}He asks for a fortune. then
disappears. Find him fast.

989
01:10:41.340 --> 01:10:43.600
{\an8}That means we're not the only
ones who suspect Kang Jae Gyeong.

990
01:10:43.640 --> 01:10:45.209
{\an8}It also means there's
hospital CCTV footage...

991
01:10:45.210 --> 01:10:46.570
{\an8}from the day of Father's accident.

992
01:10:46.640 --> 01:10:48.040
{\an8}You're dead meat. Kang Jae Gyeong.

993
01:10:48.110 --> 01:10:50.450
{\an8}Unbelievable. The whole world suspects me.

994
01:10:50.510 --> 01:10:52.250
{\an8}Are you hiding something from me?

995
01:10:52.550 --> 01:10:53.820
{\an8}There was someone else there...

996
01:10:54.120 --> 01:10:55.120
{\an8}that day.
